column5: Auger mount broke today. Lost the auger.      If anyone finds it there will be a reward for its safe return.  The mount broke somewhere between my hut, and the 7th line of Innisfil. (huts 2.5 kms straight out from the 7th)  Auger is a Jiffy 2hp lightning with a 9 inch blade. Thanks in advance.  Matt, 647-294-5982
Hopefully someone on here found it and you get it back.  Good luck.
